section.def:
board
                (董事會) means the board of directors of the
            corporation;

committee
                (委員會) means any committee of the corporation
            established by or under the constitution;

constitution
                (章程) means the constitution of the
            corporation;

corporation
                (法團) means the corporation established by
                section 3;

president
                (會長) means the president of the
            corporation;

paragraph.content:
the name and address of any person appointed under section 5 to
                    sign contracts and other instruments and any change therein, certified as
                    correct by the president;
